data.title: COVID-19 in-language and translated resources
data.meta_description: In-language educational resources on COVID-19 for health workers, communities, businesses and people in NSW.
data.text:
In-language and translated COVID-19 resources

In-language information, posters, factsheets and graphics on COVID-19 for health workers, community groups, businesses and people in NSW.

Free health advice and support in your language

Image

Easy Read COVID-19 information

Information about COVID-19 in easy to read formats with pictures and words.

east

Image

Use TIS National telephone interpreters

If you need an interpreter, call 131 450 and state the language you need.

east

Image

Information in your language from NSW Health

Translated and in-language resources on NSW Health's website.

east

Image

Information in your language from SBS

Australia's multicultural broadcaster SBS has COVID-19 infographics, factsheets, videos and resources in up to 63 languages.
